A Lightweight Hardware Security SoC for Fabless Tapeout:
Three-Layer Protection Architecture Based on RO-PUF,
Anomaly-Detection FSM, and ARX Hash Engine
面向Fabless流片的轻量级硬件安全SoC设计与验证 ——基于RO-PUF、异常检测FSM与ARX哈希的三层防护架构（硅锻-安全-SoC）
